@using EduVentureMubarakWebApp.Components.Components.Accordion

<section class="p-5 bg-light">
    <h3 class="display-6 text-primary fw-bold text-center mb-5">Frequently asked questions</h3>
    <div class="container">
        <Accordion>
            <AccordionItem Title="Can I try EduVenture Mubarak Plus first to make sure it’s right for me?">
                <p>Yes! We offer a 7-day free trial of EduVenture Mubarak Plus. During this period, you’ll have full access to all the features and content available. This allows you to explore everything we offer and decide if it's the right fit for you before committing.</p>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="What is included in EduVenture Mubarak Plus?">
                <p>EduVenture Mubarak Plus includes access to our entire library of educational resources—covering subjects such as literacy, mathematics, sciences, and technology. You’ll also gain access to our interactive digital platform, live sessions with educators, and exclusive certificates upon course completion. Whether you're looking for traditional learning materials or advanced digital tools, EduVenture Mubarak Plus has everything you need.</p>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="Will I save money with EduVenture Mubarak Plus?">
                <p>Yes, by subscribing to EduVenture Mubarak Plus, you’ll enjoy significant savings compared to purchasing individual courses or specializations. With one subscription, you get unlimited access to all content, which means more learning for less!</p>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="How many certificates can I earn with EduVenture Mubarak Plus?">
                <p>There’s no limit! With EduVenture Mubarak Plus, you can earn an unlimited number of certificates. As long as you complete the courses and meet the requirements, you can collect certificates in a wide variety of subjects and specializations.</p>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="What can I do with my certificates once I’ve earned them?">
                <p>Your certificates from EduVenture Mubarak hold value in several ways. You can:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Enhance your resume and showcase your new skills to employers.</li>
                    <li>Share your achievements on professional platforms like LinkedIn.</li>
                    <li>Use them to demonstrate your qualifications for job opportunities or further studies.</li>
                    <li>Gain personal recognition and build your confidence in your educational journey.</li>
                </ul>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="Can I get reimbursed by my employer for EduVenture Mubarak?">
                <p>In some cases, yes! Many employers offer education reimbursement programs. We recommend checking with your HR department or manager to see if your EduVenture Mubarak subscription qualifies for reimbursement under your company's professional development or education program.</p>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="What happens to my existing EduVenture Mubarak Specialization subscription when I subscribe to EduVenture Mubarak Plus?">
                <p>If you already have an EduVenture Mubarak Specialization subscription, it will be automatically upgraded to EduVenture Mubarak Plus. You’ll keep your progress in all the courses you’ve started and gain access to even more content without needing to reenroll in any courses you were already working on.</p>
            </AccordionItem>
            <AccordionItem Title="Will EduVenture Mubarak Plus motivate me to learn?">
                <p>Absolutely! EduVenture Mubarak Plus offers a gamified learning experience with points, badges, and rewards for achieving milestones. You’ll also have access to a community of learners to share your journey with, creating a motivating and engaging environment to help you stay on track and reach your learning goals.</p>
            </AccordionItem>
        </Accordion>
    </div>
</section>